BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Indivisible Sonoma County Out-of-District Team
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260420T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260420T190000
UID:2d0c4529ed2cbf93c3a50bb858503dd3@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Turning%20Congress%20Blue_20260107203453834038.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The OOD group works to preserve blue and flip red seats. We've
  worked on both national and state races. We write postcards\, canvas\, te
 xt\, fundraise\, register voters\, phone banks\, research\, and coordinate
  with campaigns and political action groups. New members are always welcom
 e! Our get-togethers are informative meetings that discuss our plans to co
 ntinue holding the California districts we flipped in the last election\, 
 as well as to convert the remaining red districts in the upcoming election
 .
LOCATION:Virtual event
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblesonomacounty/event/881687/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
